&lt;p data-start=&quot;1735&quot; data-end=&quot;1801&quot;&gt;Proficient in Python and skilled at data processing and analysis&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1802&quot; data-end=&quot;1891&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1804&quot; data-end=&quot;1891&quot;&gt;Passionate about quantitative finance, curious, innovative, and able to learn quickly&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1892&quot; data-end=&quot;1965&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1894&quot; data-end=&quot;1965&quot;&gt;Able to work well under pressure; strong communicator and team player&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
